Package ``apache-airflow-providers-ssh``

Release: ``3.5.0``


`Secure Shell (SSH) <https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4251>`__


Provider package
----------------

This is a provider package for ``ssh`` provider. All classes for this provider package
are in ``airflow.providers.ssh`` python package.

You can find package information and changelog for the provider
in the `documentation <https://airflow.apache.org/docs/apache-airflow-providers-ssh/3.5.0/>`_.


Installation
------------

You can install this package on top of an existing Airflow 2 installation (see ``Requirements`` below
for the minimum Airflow version supported) via
``pip install apache-airflow-providers-ssh``

The package supports the following python versions: 3.7,3.8,3.9,3.10

Requirements
------------

==================  ==================
PIP package         Version required
==================  ==================
``apache-airflow``  ``>=2.3.0``
``paramiko``        ``>=2.6.0``
``sshtunnel``       ``>=0.3.2``
==================  ==================
